Given the perimeter of the pond \(=a\),
\[
\begin{array}{l}
2y+x+\frac{1}{2}\pi x=a \\
2y+\left(1+\frac{1}{2}\pi\right)x=a \\
y=\frac{2a-(2+\pi)x}{4}
\end{array}
\]

The area of the pond is
\[
\begin{array}{c}
L=xy+\frac{1}{8}\pi x^2 \\
L=x\left(\frac{2a-(2+\pi)x}{4}\right)+\frac{1}{8}\pi x^2 \\
L=\frac{4ax-(4+2\pi)x^2+\pi x^2}{8} \\
L=\frac{4ax-(4+\pi)x^2}{8}
\end{array}
\]

The condition for maximum area \(L'=0\) is
\[
\begin{array}{c}
L'=(4a-2(4+\pi)x)=0 \\
x=\frac{2a}{4+\pi}
\end{array}
\] 

Answer: \(x=\frac{2a}{4+\pi}\)

raw_answer:
Diketahui keliling kolam \( =a \)
\[
\begin{array}{l}
2 y+x+\frac{1}{2} \pi x=a \\
2 y+\left(1+\frac{1}{2} \pi\right) x=a \\
y=\frac{2 a-(2+\pi) x}{4}
\end{array}
\]

Luas kolam adalah
\[
\begin{array}{c}
L=x y+\frac{1}{8} \pi x^{2} \\
L=x\left(\frac{2 a-(2+\pi) x}{4}\right)+\frac{1}{8} \pi x^{2} \\
L=\frac{4 a x-(4+2 \pi) x^{2}+\pi x^{2}}{8} \\
L=\frac{4 a x-(4+\pi) x^{2}}{8}
\end{array}
\]

Syarat luas kolam maksimum \( L^{\prime}=0 \)
\[
\begin{array}{c}
L^{\prime}=(4 a-2(4+\pi) x=0 \\
x=\frac{2 a}{4+\pi}
\end{array}
\]

