Agar \( k \) maksimum, maka \( f(x) \) harus maksimum. Sehingga syarat maksimum \( f^{\prime}(x)=0 \)
\[
\begin{array}{c}
f^{\prime}(x)=\frac{2 \cos \theta}{\sin ^{2} \theta}+\cos \theta=0 \\
\cos \theta\left(\frac{2}{\sin ^{2} \theta}+1\right)=0 \\
\cos \theta=0 \\
\theta=\frac{\pi}{2}
\end{array}
\]

Selanjutnya \( \theta=\frac{\pi}{2} \) substitusi ke \( f(x) \)
\[
\text { Jadi, } \begin{aligned}
k_{\text {maks }} & =f_{\text {maks }}=\frac{2}{\sin \frac{\pi}{2}}+\sin \frac{\pi}{2} \\
& =\frac{2}{1}+1=3
\end{aligned}
\]

